<a id="Shiv Surya" class="anchor" href="#Shiv Surya" aria-hidden="true"><span aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Shiv Surya</h3> 


<p style="text-align:justify">
I am a Research Staff Member with <a href="http://www.serc.iisc.ernet.in/~venky/">Prof.Venkatesh Babu's</a> lab in <a href="www.iisc.ernet.in/">Indian Institute of Science</a> in Bangalore, India, working on machine learning and computer vision. I received my M.S in Electrical Engineering from <a href="https://www.usc.edu/">University of Southern California</a> in 2015. At USC, I worked in <a href="http://sail.usc.edu/shri.php">Shrikanth Narayanan's</a> lab on liveness deteciton in speech. I obtained B.E degree in Electrical Engineering from <a href="www.rvce.edu.in/">RVCE</a> in 2013.
<h3>
<a id="research-interest" class="anchor" href="#research-interest" aria-hidden="true"><span aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Research Interest</h3>

<p style="text-align:justify">My main research interests are in machine learning applied to computer vision and speech. In particular, I am interested in learning strategies for deep learning, generalized object detection and cross-depiction</p>

